com.facebook.buck.parser

Interface Parser


  • public interface Parser
    High-level build file parsing machinery. Primarily responsible for producing a TargetGraph based on a set of targets. Caches build rules to minimise the number of calls to build file interpreter and processes filesystem events to invalidate the cache as files change.
